## Resources

- **Team**: Project Manager (1), Lead Developer (1), Data Scientist (1), Frontend Developer (1), Principal Investigator (1) – all part-time (20% effort).  
- **Computing**: Cloud credits for testing (AWS/GCP) – $500 budget.  
- **Data**: Public datasets from GEO (GSE series) and TCGA – free.  
- **Tools**: Python, R, Git, GitHub Actions, Plotly/Dash, LaTeX.  

## Communication

