## Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)

- **Code coverage**: ≥80% by end of Phase 2.  
- **Pipeline accuracy**: ≥90% on synthetic data, ≥80% on real data (age correlation).  
- **Database size**: ≥100 curated markers by end of Phase 3.  
- **Dashboard uptime**: ≥99% during review period.  
- **Publication**: Manuscript submitted within 2 weeks of Phase 3 completion.  

